---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="CC Routes | High Capacity Call Center Routes - My Call Connect" description="Specialized CC routes for high-volume call centers. CLI and NCLI options with high ASR/ACD and unlimited concurrent calls.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-ring ring-1 hide-on-mobile"></div>
      <div class="hero-ring ring-2 hide-on-mobile"></div>
      
      <div class="hero-content animate-up">
        <span class="badge">High Volume Traffic</span>
        <h1>CC Routes & <br><span class="text-gradient">Dialer Termination</span></h1>
        <p class="delay-1 animate-up">Specialized routes designed for the unique needs of call centers. High CPS, unlimited ports, and stable connections for your dialer traffic.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta delay-2 animate-up">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Rate Sheet <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg></a>
          <a href="#specs" class="text-link">Tech Specs</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="specs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Engineered for <span class="text-gradient-primary">Performance</span></h2>
        <p>Don't let congestion block your sales. Our network handles bursts effortlessly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <!-- High CPS -->
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>High CPS Support</h3>
          <p>Blast thousands of calls per second without blockage. Our infrastructure is built for predictive dialers.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-500 mb-6 list-none">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Unlimited Channels</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Burst Handling</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> No FAS</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Route Options -->
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Flexible Routing</h3>
          <p>Choose between Premium CLI for sales or cost-effective NCLI for surveys and notifications.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-500 mb-6 list-none">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> CLI Routes</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> NCLI Routes</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> TDM Interconnects</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Stability -->
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"></line><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"></line></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Maximum Stability</h3>
          <p>Keep your agents talking. We maintain high Average Seizure Rate (ASR) and call duration.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-500 mb-6 list-none">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> High ASR</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> High ACD</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Redundant POPs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Compatible with All <span class="text-gradient-primary">Dialers</span></h2>
          <p class="section-desc">Our SIP trunks are certified to work with all major call center software and PBX systems.</p>
          
          <div class="feature-list mt-8">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-item-num">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polygon points="10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8"></polygon></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3>Vicidial / GoAutoDial</h3>
                <p>Fully optimized for Asterisk-based dialers with sample configuration guides provided.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-item-num">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"></path><line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"></line></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3>3CX / FreePBX</h3>
                <p>Seamless integration with standard SIP-based PBX systems for enterprise call centers.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-item-num">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3>Cloud Contact Centers</h3>
                <p>Connect easily to Genesys, Five9, Talkdesk, and other cloud platforms via SIP.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-image">
          <div class="content-icon">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Traffic Monitoring</h3>
          <p>Real-time stats to keep your campaigns performing at their peak.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container-sm">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <span class="badge badge-light">Boost Your Sales</span>
          <h2>Optimize Your Call Center Traffic</h2>
          <p>Stop losing leads to failed calls. Switch to My Call Connect's premium CC routes today.</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-light">Contact Sales</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-white">Test Routes</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
